Package: ggsegCraddock
Title: Craddock Functional Parcellations for the 'ggseg' Ecosystem
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Athanasia Mo", "Mowinckel", , "a.m.mowinckel@psykologi.uio.no", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5756-0223"))
  )
Description: Craddock spatially constrained spectral clustering parcellations
    at various resolutions for the 'ggseg' ecosystem. Provides a unified
    'ggseg_atlas' object with both 2D polygon geometry and 3D vertex indices,
    for use with 'ggseg' and 'ggseg3d'.
License: CC0
Encoding: UTF-8
