    R (>= 3.5),
    ggseg.formats
Suggests:
    ggseg,
    ggseg3d,
    ggplot2,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    vdiffr
Remotes:
    ggseg/ggseg,
    ggseg/ggseg3d,
    ggseg/ggseg.formats
